Wild_txt1: FU BAT symbol is wild and substitutes for all symbols. FU BAT only appears on reels 2, 3, and 4.
SpecialPays_text2: All wins pay in any position from left to right on adjacent reels, beginning with the leftmost reel.
SpecialPays_text4: One or more FU BAT in a winning combination is wild and substitutes for all symbols.
SpecialPays_text5: The gold symbols played are displayed in the Active Symbols Area.
SpecialPays_text6: Each of the gold symbols are played on alternate sets of reels.
Fubat_text1: When one or more FU BAT appears, the player may be awarded an available jackpot.
Fubat_text2: The number of gold symbols played determines eligibility for jackpot wins.
Fubat_text3: If the player is eligible for more than one jackpot, they will be taken to a separate screen where 12 coins will appear.
Fubat_text4: Touching or clicking a coin will reveal the symbol of an available jackpot.
Fubat_text5: When 3 matching symbols have been revealed, the corresponding jackpot will be awarded and the feature ends.
Fubat_text6: Jackpot values are proportional to bet per spin.
FreeGames_text1: 3, 4 or 5 GONG symbols on adjacent reels, starting with the leftmost reel, award 10 free games.
FreeGames_text2: ACE, KING, QUEEN, JACK, 10 and 9 do not appear during free games.
FreeGames_text3: Bet per spin and the number of gold symbols chosen are same as the spin when the free games were triggered.
FreeGames_text4: The Fu Bat Jackpot Feature can be triggered inside the free games.
FreeGames_text5: Additional free games may be awarded during the Free Games Feature and are added to the remaining free games.
FreeGames_text6: The Free Games Feature ends when no free games remain.
FreeGames_text7: The Free Games Feature is played on an alternate set of reels.
AnyWay_text1: Bet ways win when matching symbols appear anywhere on adjacent reels from the leftmost to the rightmost.
AnyWay_text2: Only highest win per bet way is paid.
AnyWay_text3: All symbols pay as described in the paytable.
AnyWay_text4: The paytable is dynamic and reflects actual payouts based on current wager.
AnyWay_text5: Wins on different ways are added together and scatter wins (if available) are added to way wins.
AnyWay_text6: Malfunction Voids all pays and plays.
AnyWay_text7: The theoretical average return to player(RTP) is
AnyWay_text8: This RTP represents the long-term expected payback of the game which has been calculated by an independent testing company, in accordance with required regulations.
AnyWay_text9: Any combination of wins in a single game is limited and will not exceed {0}
AnyWay_text10: It may not be possible to reach this limit in a single game from every stake configuration
